    IConflict, IDataStructurePB

    public class ConflictMapReduceToCard
extends ConflictMap
    This class implements the reduction to cardinality algorithm proposed by Heidi Dixon in her dissertation. Procedure 4.3.9 page 67, in Automating pseudo-boolean inference within a DPLL framework, Ph.D. thesis by Heidi Dixon, University of Oregon, December 2004
